node.text:
The harder the battle, the sweeter the victory 👑 

For the @pho3nixife Sub8 Project, I will face many battles.
The battle with history,
The battle with my limits,
And the battle with my rival - @nicolaspirigofficial 

This is going to be a whole new push on what’s possible but I am ready to take on the battle and prove what I can do 🥇

#DefyTheImpossible  #Pho3nix  #Sub7Sub8  #Triathlon 
🎬 @mana.studios  @orbitalstud.io |

node.text:
Messy bun = getting stuff done💁🏼‍♀️
Not everyday is a #BattleBraids kind of day but the show must go on!☺️
The gym is my happy place, progress is easily tangible & I love seeing just how strong I can get💪🏻
If you haven’t seen my latest video on strength & conditioning for triathletes then hit the link in my bio🔗🎥
📸: @hollycharlesphotography_ 
#spottheknot #GivesYouWings #strongwomen #strongnotskinny #girlpower #livetoinspire #clublasanta #lanzarote #strengthtraining #girlswholift #trichicks #crossfit #BloodSweatandData #knowledgeisprogress  #TeamCharlesBarclay
